bilingual.source: The shell of a turtle is very hard.
The shell of the tortoise is very hard.
The shell of the egg is very fragile.
The shell of a tortoise is very hard.
The snail carries its shell on its back.
The shell of an armadillo is very hard.
The shell of this beetle is green.
bilingual.target: 这只甲壳虫的壳是绿色的。

list.abstract: 壳层（英语：Shell）在计算机科学中，是指“提供用户使用界面”的软件，通常指的是命令行界面的解析器。一般来说，这个词是指操作系统中，提供访问内核所提供之服务的程序。不过这个词也拿来指应用软件，或是任何在特定组件外围的软件，例如浏览器或电子邮件软件是HTML排版引擎的shell。Shell这个词是来自于操作系统（内核）与用户界面的外层界面。通常将壳层分为两类：命令行与图形界面。命令行壳层提供一个命令行界面（CLI）；而图形壳层提供一个图形用户界面（GUI）。
shell，英语单词，名词、及物动词、不及物动词，作名词时意为“壳，贝壳；炮弹；外形”，作及物动词时意为“剥皮；炮轰”，作不及物动词时意为“剥落；设定命令行解释器的位置”。

yingyinNormal.en: You, go to Shell City?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你，去贝壳城？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Where has he gone? He's hiding in his shell. Is that where he lives? Yes, it's his house. Look, he's coming out again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他到哪里去了？他躲到壳里去了。那是他住的地方吗？是的，那是他的房子。看，他又从壳里出来了。

yingyinNormal.en: She's so hot, I can feel my shell tightening. We can hear you!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他长得实在太火辣了， 我感觉我的壳都缩紧了。我们能听得到。

yingyinNormal.en: That shell is his house. It's very high if he gets hurt. Would you like to stroke him?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个壳就是他的家。当他感到害怕的时候就会躲进去。你们想要摸摸他吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Hello Tiddles. Tiddles has slept all through the winter. Why has he got that shell thing on his back?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好啊，小土豆！知道吗，小土豆已经睡了一整个冬天了。哇。他为什么要背一个壳在身上呢？

yingyinNormal.en: The easiest way to do that is to lay it flat on there and just make two slits into the shell and then that's still together so we can just...
yingyinNormal.zh: 最简单的方法是把它在这放平，然后在壳上切两道口，但它们仍然连在一起，我们只要……

yingyinNormal.en: Shell City. Yeah, we never made it to Shell City. Shell City. Exactly, buddy. Yeah, the place we never got to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 贝壳城。是啊，我们根本没到贝壳城。对，兄弟。对，我们从来没到过的地方。

yingyinNormal.en: Shell City is a gift shop? But if this is Shell City, then where's the...?
yingyinNormal.zh: 贝壳城是个礼品店？但是如果这个是贝壳城，那么皇冠……？

yingyinNormal.en: No, look at the sign. Shell City. Marine gifts and sundries.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，看看那个标志。贝壳城，海洋产品、礼品和杂货。

yingyinNormal.en: Shell City. Okay, now you're starting to bum me out, Patrick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 贝壳城。你有点让我厌烦了，派崔克。

yingyinNormal.en: Crown. Neptune's crown. This is Shell City. Pat, we did make it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 皇冠。海王星的皇冠。这就是贝壳城。派特，我们成功了。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we're not gonna get the crown standing here. On to Shell City.
yingyinNormal.zh: 光站在这里是拿不到皇冠的。去贝壳城吧。

yingyinNormal.en: It is. I saw the construction. The outer wall is a shell. There is no fortification.
yingyinNormal.zh: 波罗先生。是的，我亲眼所见，外墙不过是个空壳，没有设防。

yingyinNormal.en: Quiet, fool! Mr. Krabs stole my crown, and now it's in Shell City. That's why he must die.
yingyinNormal.zh: 闭嘴，笨蛋，克莱伯偷了我的皇冠，现在皇冠在贝壳城。所以他必须死。

yingyinNormal.en: No one who's gone to Shell City has ever returned. What makes you think you could? You're just a kid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没人能从贝壳城活着回来，你凭什么认为你行？你只是个小孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: I made it to Shell City, and I beat the Cyclops, and I rode the Hasselhoff, and I brought the crown back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我去到了贝壳城，我打败了独眼巨人，我骑上了哈斯霍夫，我把皇冠拿回来了。

yingyinNormal.en: Listen, you guys, the road to Shell City is really dangerous. There's crooks, killers and monsters everywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，通往贝壳城的道路非常危险。那里有骗子，杀手，到处都是怪兽。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, first of all, this isn't a restaurant. Secondly, my bisque had a tooth in it. It was a shell. There was a filling in it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先，这里不是饭店，其次，那是因为那份浓汤里有一颗牙。是贝壳。那是实心的。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm starting to feel like you attaching yourself to something that's not a calculated act is just too much for your empty human shell to handle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我开始觉得好像你总是把自己依附于不真实的事情上你空虚的人类躯壳负担不起这种做作的表演。

yingyinNormal.en: Danny has found a pine cone. Treasure. Peppa has found a shell. Treasure. Suzy has found an old bit of rope. Treasure. Freddy has found a pebble. Treasure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 丹尼发现了一个松果。宝藏。佩奇发现了一个贝壳。宝藏。苏西发现了一截旧的绳子。宝藏。弗莱迪发现了一个鹅卵石。宝藏。

sense_info_list.en: the hard outer part of eggs, nuts, some seeds and some animals
any object that looks like the shell of a snail or sea creature

word_usage.usage: shell作名词，表示“表面性格，表面人格，外表”时，常用单数形式，如：a shell of indifference 冷漠的外壳。
shell作动词时需要注意熟词僻义，表示“炮击”，如：shell the city 空袭城市。
